title: Stanford O-line wreaks havoc, McCaffrey has big game vs. Beavers
text:
Photo: Steve Dykes, Getty Images Stanford running back Christian McCaffrey (5) dives as Beavers safety Justin Strong (4) tackles him. McCaffrey rushed 206 yards on 30 carries, caught a 38-yard pass, returned a kickoff 31 yards. Stanford running back Christian McCaffrey (5) dives as Beavers...
CORVALLIS, Ore. — Call it “a 6.8 yards and a cloud of dust’’ rushing offense. That’s mainly what No. 21 Stanford used in throttling Oregon State on Friday night. Stanford running back Christian McCaffrey (5) dives as Beavers safety Justin Strong (4) tackles him. McCaffrey rushed 206 yards on 30 carries, caught a 38-yard pass, returned a kickoff 31 yards.
